Global Osmium Tetroxide Market Insights
Osmium Tetroxide Market size was valued at USD 0.30 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.50 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Osmium Tetroxide Market Overview
The Osmium Tetroxide market has seen significant growth due to its increasing applications in various industries such as chemistry, electronics, and medical research. As of 2024, the global market value for Osmium Tetroxide was approximately USD 100 million and is projected to expand at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2025 to 2030. The growth is largely driven by its unique properties and its essential role in the synthesis of complex organic compounds and as a key reagent in electron microscopy. Additionally, rising demand from emerging economies has contributed to market expansion, with North America and Europe holding dominant shares in the market.

